introduction 1 the plaintiff, stephen asciak, applies to the court pursuant to s 198f(2) of the corporations act 2001 (cth) for orders that he be permitted to inspect, and take copies of, the books of each of the four defendant companies (including their financial records) for the financial years ending 30 june 2004, 30 june 2005 and 30 june 2006 and take copies of them.
